uk 可能試下睇brothers karamazov或者人間喜劇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雜食喎巴打，本身修文學？<br />\n你講嘅呢幾本我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過poetry collection 會多啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba12ccf7a07a01f20860d90efe946b83e4e0bb16","tid":941,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:34:28.000Z","msg":"有冇咩書好推介？"},{"pid":"7b4634d7cd753d19af860691c44603a34c57f835","tid":941,"uid":17283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:17:23.000Z","msg":"同好留名"},{"pid":"1df9d401a8012b11966b85ebe92728545949ed82","tid":941,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇咩書好推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想要novel, short stories collection 定係poetry collection？"},{"pid":"dd2ecb592123a642a096473341dbd750a10bf096","tid":941,"uid":4706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意百年孤寂<br />\n呢排睇緊Orhan Pamuk</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nM&aacute;rquez唔錯喎，早期嘅magic realism。<br />\nPamuk係睇緊My name is red?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMy name is red幾年前睇完<br />\n睇緊museum of innocence</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦，Pamuk我真係少留意，主要係講conflict between East and West?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢講tradition同modern比較出色<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多鍾意既小說同作家<br />\nDubliners,crime and punishment,catcher in the rye,Calvino<br />\n數唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完Pamuk 可能試下睇brothers karamazov或者人間喜劇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雜食喎巴打，本身修文學？<br />\n你講嘅呢幾本我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過poetry collection 會多啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身中文系<br />\n但對外國文學愈睇愈上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc67e580f2f5b906169658fc47300750a58fc516","tid":941,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意百年孤寂<br />\n呢排睇緊Orhan Pamuk</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nM&aacute;rquez唔錯喎，早期嘅magic realism。<br />\nPamuk係睇緊My name is red?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMy name is red幾年前睇完<br />\n睇緊museum of innocence</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦，Pamuk我真係少留意，主要係講conflict between East and West?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢講tradition同modern比較出色<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多鍾意既小說同作家<br />\nDubliners,crime and punishment,catcher in the rye,Calvino<br />\n數唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完Pamuk 可能試下睇brothers karamazov或者人間喜劇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雜食喎巴打，本身修文學？<br />\n你講嘅呢幾本我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過poetry collection 會多啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身中文系<br />\n但對外國文學愈睇愈上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好少中文系同學對西方文學有興趣喎，因為大部分都覺得係奇技淫巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}